location.fullValue: Hadley Plan, High Point at Foxbank

data.description: Killarney Trail is a secluded part of Foxbank Plantation with most traffic being your neighbors that live on that street too. This lot backs up to the woods and the lot across the street is wooded. Downstairs is open concept with dining area, kitchen, and living space. Upstairs are the 2 bedrooms plus the primary suite. The back yard is fenced in an ready for your enjoyment in privacy. Foxbank has its own Elementary School that provides for  grades k5-5th grade #goboykins! The neighborhood amenities are TWO olympic size pools, play ground, shelter to host cook outs, a lake with docks, dog park, walking trails, and a community garden.
